htmlContent.name: barGraph
htmlContent.content:
<div>
<style type="text/css">
.barGraph {
  max-width: 100%;
  max-height: 280px;
}
.barGraph .legend rect {
  cursor: pointer;
  stroke-width: 1;
}
.barGraph rect.disabled {
  fill: #d9d9d9 !important;
}

.barGraph rect {
  shape-rendering: crispEdges;
}
.barGraph .slice {
  cursor: pointer;
}
.barGraph .slice.disabled {
  fill: #d9d9d9;
}
.barGraph .tick text {
  fill: #6B7070; 
}
.barGraph rect:not(.mouseRect) {
  fill: #005aa0;
}

.barGraph text {
  fill: #d3d3d3;
  font: 10px Arial;
  text-anchor: end;
}

.barGraph .axis text {
  fill: #6B7070;
  font: 10px Arial;
}

.barGraph .axis path,
.barGraph .axis line {
  fill: none;
  stroke: #f3f3f3;
  stroke-width: 1px;
  shape-rendering: crispEdges;
}
.barGraph #line4 {
  fill: none;
  stroke: #f3f3f3;
  stroke-width: 2px;
}

.barGraph rect:not(.mouseRect) {
  fill: #005aa0;
}

.barGraph text {
  fill: #d3d3d3;
  font: 10px Arial;
  text-anchor: end;
}
.barGraph .tick {
  color: #6B7070;
}
.barGraph .y.axis .tick line {
  opacity: 0.1;
}

.barGraph .mouseRectText {
  font-family: "Intro Cond";
  fill: white;
}

.barGraph .legendText {
  font-family: "Intro Cond"
}

.barGraph .area {
  stroke-width: 0;
}
</style>
 <svg class="barGraph"></svg>
 <div>
